[Play "Pitch Back"]
[Badge "opening rush"]
[Call "Pitch back"]
[Desc "Opening rush. The two right players grab our three center-line balls (one grabs two, one grabs one), then pitch one back to an attacker who steps up to mid-court and picks off a backpedaling rusher."]
[Setup "rush"]

1. {Rush — the two on the right grab our three (2 + 1)} :1.3  U7-line U8-line U8*2 U7* T1-line T2-line T1*2 T2*
2. {Pitch back — rushers regress as the attacker steps up} :0.9  U8>U5 U78-deep U5-68 T12-deep
3. {Free look — hit a regressing rusher} :1  U5@T2! U78-back T12-back
